					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I think the practical ideas are cutting data and code that isn't part of the test, and unique roms per tester like hidden data and/or unique offsets of code and data.
<br />
<br />But whatever you do don't try too hard. I suppose if you were really serious about protecting a NES game you'd be best off with a highly customized mapper.</div>

